{
  "chapter": "058",
  "title": "梁孝王世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "梁孝王身世",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>刘武，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文皇帝</span>的儿子，和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景帝</span>同母。母亲，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "文帝四子",
      "text": "孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>共有四个儿子：长子为太子，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景帝</span>；次子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘武\">武（刘武）</span>；次子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘参\">参（刘参）</span>；次子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胜\">胜（刘胜）</span>。孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>即位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘武\">武（刘武）</span>为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>王，立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘参\">参（刘参）</span>为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太原</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胜\">胜（刘胜）</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁怀王\">梁王（梁怀王）</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>后，将<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>王改封为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮阳</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>全部并入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太原</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>的封国，号称<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘参\">参（刘参）</span>立<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十七年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">孝文（汉文帝）</span>后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>去世，谥为孝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘登\">登（刘登）</span>嗣立，就是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">代</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：代共王\">共王（代共王）</span>。在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十九年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元光</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>去世。其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘义\">义（刘义）</span>继立，就是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>王。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十九年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>扩大关中范围，以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>为界，把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>王改封为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">清河</span>王。改封<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">清河</span>王是在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元鼎</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "徙封梁王",
      "text": "起初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘武\">武（刘武）</span>做<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮阳</span>王<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十年（时长）</span>时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胜\">胜（刘胜）</span>去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁怀王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁怀王\">怀王（梁怀王）</span>是文帝最小的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span>，受宠爱超过其他<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>。第二年，把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮阳</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘武\">武（刘武）</span>改封为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>初封<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>的时候，是孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>的<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>自初<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>已经经历了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十一年（时长）</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "入朝承欢",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，入朝。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十七年（时长）</span>、<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十八年</span>，连年入朝留京，第二年才<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">回到封国</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十一年</span>，入朝。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十二年</span>，孝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>驾崩。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十四年</span>，入朝。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十五年</span>，再入朝。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">上（汉景帝）</span>还未立<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">上（汉景帝）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宴饮</span>时，曾闲谈说：\"我千秋万岁之后，把皇位传给王。\"王推辞。虽然知道这不是最终的安排，但心里高兴。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span>也是如此。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "抗御吴楚",
      "text": "那年<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">春</span>天，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">七国</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>先<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">棘壁</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万人</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>据城守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">睢阳</span>，任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩安国</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张羽</span>等为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>，以抵<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>所阻，不敢越过西进，与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周亚夫\">亚夫（周亚夫）</span>等相持<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三月（时长）</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">被破</span>，而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>所<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">打败</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘</span>的约与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝各占一半。第二年，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>立太子。其后<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>最为亲近，有功，又是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">大国</span>，据有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>膏腴之地。地北界<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泰山</span>，西至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高阳</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十馀城</span>，都是大县。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "恩宠至极",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>的小儿子，深受宠爱，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赏赐</span>之多不可胜数。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>修筑东苑，方圆<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百馀里</span>。扩建<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">睢阳</span>城<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十里</span>。大造<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宫室</span>，修<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">复道</span>，从宫殿连通到平台<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十馀里</span>。得赐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旌旗</span>，出行<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千乘万骑</span>跟从。东西<span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">驰骋打猎</span>，比拟<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。出入时宣告清道<span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">跸</span><span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">警</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "招延豪桀",
      "text": "招揽四方<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪桀</span>，崤山以东的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">游说之士</span>，无不毕至，如<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羊胜</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">公孙</span>诡、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邹阳</span>之属。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">公孙</span>诡多有奇邪之计，初见王时，获赐千<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>，官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国号称<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">公孙</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国多造<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵器</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弩</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弓</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">矛</span>达<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十万</span>，而<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">府库</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span>将近百亿，珠<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝器</span>多过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "入朝同辇",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十九年（时长）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十月</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>入朝。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>派使者持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乘舆</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">驷马</span>，在关下迎接<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">梁王</span>。朝见之后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">上（汉景帝）</span>疏因留他在京，因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span>的缘故。王入宫则侍<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>同<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">辇</span>，出宫则同<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>游猎，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上林</span>苑中射<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">禽兽</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侍中</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谒者</span>登记在册，可出入<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>殿门，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝宦官无异。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "储位之议",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一月</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">上（汉景帝）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗太子</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>心中想立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>为嗣。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>等有话向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>进言，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>的主张被阻，也就不再提立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>为嗣的事，原因正在于此。因事秘密，世人不知。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>告辞归国。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "刺杀袁盎",
      "text": "那年<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">夏</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">上（汉景帝）</span>立<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">胶东</span>王为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>怨恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>及参议此事的大臣，就和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羊胜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙诡</span>等人阴谋派刺客<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>及其他议臣共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀人</span>。追捕凶手，未能抓获。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>怀疑是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>所为，追查凶手，果然是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>派去的。于是接连派出使者，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">冠盖</span>在路上相望，覆按<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国情况，要〖[捕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙诡</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羊胜</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙诡</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羊胜</span>藏匿在王的后宫。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">使者</span>严责<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>急查，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>相<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩丘豹</span>和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩安国</span>进谏王，王就命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：羊胜\">胜（羊胜）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙诡\">诡（公孙诡）</span>都〖[自杀，交出尸体。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">上（汉景帝）</span>从此怨恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>害怕，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩安国</span>通过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太主\">长公主（窦太主）</span>向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span>谢罪，然后才得〖[释。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "匿车谢罪",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">上（汉景帝）</span>的怒气稍解，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>因此上书请求入朝。到了关口，茅<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">兰</span>劝王乘布<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，只带<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两骑</span>进入，藏在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太主\">长公主（窦太主）</span>的园中。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>派使者去迎接王，王已入关，车骑都留在外面，不知王在哪里。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>哭着说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">帝（汉景帝）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了我儿子！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>忧虑恐惧。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>伏在<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">斧质</span>于宫阙下，谢罪，然后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>大喜，相对哭泣，恢复如故。把王的随从全召入关。然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>更加疏远王，不再同<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">辇</span>了。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "王薨哀悼",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十五年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">冬</span>，又入朝。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">上（汉景帝）</span>疏，王想留下来，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">上（汉景帝）</span>不允。回国后，心情郁郁不乐。北上到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">良山</span><span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">打猎</span>，有人献<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>，脚长在背上，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>厌恶这种怪象。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六月</span>中，患热病，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六天</span>后去世，谥曰孝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "分梁五国",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>慈孝，每听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span>生病，口不能食，居不安寝，常想留在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>侍<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>也爱他。等听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span><span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">薨</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>哭得极哀，不吃东西，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">帝（汉景帝）</span>果然<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了我儿子！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>哀伤恐惧，不知所措。和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太主\">长公主（窦太主）</span>商议对策，就把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>分为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">五国</span>，全部<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五</span>个儿子为王，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五</span>个女儿都食<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">汤沐邑</span>。于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">奏</span>告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>才高兴，替<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">帝（汉景帝）</span>加<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一餐</span>饭。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "五国分封",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>长子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘买\">买（刘买）</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁共王\">梁王（梁共王）</span>，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁共王\">共王（梁共王）</span>；子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘明\">明（刘明）</span>为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济川</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>；子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭离\">彭离（刘彭离）</span>为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济东</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>；子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘定\">定（刘定）</span>为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山阳</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>；子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘不识\">不识（刘不识）</span>为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济阴</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "藏府财富",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>未死时，财富以巨万计，不可胜数。死后，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">藏府</span>剩余的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄金</span>还有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十馀万斤</span>，其他财物也相当。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "共王继立",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁共王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>驾崩。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁共王\">共王（梁共王）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘襄\">襄（刘襄）</span>即位，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁平王\">平王（梁平王）</span>。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "罍樽之争",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁平王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘襄\">襄（刘襄）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>时，母亲称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈太后</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁共王\">共王（梁共王）</span>的母亲称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李太后</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李太后</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁平王\">平王（梁平王）</span>的祖母。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁平王\">平王（梁平王）</span>的王后姓任，叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任王后</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任王后</span>甚得<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁平王\">平王（梁平王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘襄\">襄（刘襄）</span>宠爱。起初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>在世时，有一<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">罍樽</span>，价值千<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>告诫后世，要善保此<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">罍樽</span>，不得与人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任王后</span>听说后想要此<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">罍樽</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁平王\">平王（梁平王）</span>的祖母<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李太后</span>说：\"先<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>有命，不得把<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">罍樽</span>与人。其他财物虽百亿，也任你自取。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任王后</span>执意要得。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁平王\">平王（梁平王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘襄\">襄（刘襄）</span>径直派人开<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">府</span>取<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">罍樽</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赐</span>给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任王后</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李太后</span>大怒，汉<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">使者</span>来时，她想亲自申诉，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁平王\">平王（梁平王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘襄\">襄（刘襄）</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任王后</span>阻拦，关门，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李太后</span>与他们〖[争门，〖[夹伤了手指，最终未能见到汉<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">使者</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李太后</span>也私下与食官长及<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尹霸</span>等人〖[通奸，王和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任王后</span>以此叫人暗示制止<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李太后</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李太后</span>内有淫行，也就作罢。后病薨。病时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任王后\">任后（任王后）</span>未曾探问；薨后，又不持丧。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "类犴反告发",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元朔</span>中，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">睢阳</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">类犴反</span>，有人侮辱他的父亲，当时那人正与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮阳</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太守</span>的宾客出行同坐一<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太守</span>的宾客下车时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">类犴反</span>在车上<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了他的仇人后离去。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮阳</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太守</span>大怒，以此责让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>以下紧急搜捕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：类犴反\">反（类犴反）</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">抓捕</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：类犴反\">反（类犴反）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：类犴反\">反（类犴反）</span>知道国中阴事，就上书告变，详细<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">告</span>发王与祖母争<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">罍樽</span>的事。当时<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>以下已经知情，想以此伤害<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长吏</span>，告书送到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>那里。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吏</span>核查，情况属实。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">请废<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘襄\">襄（刘襄）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李太后</span>有淫行，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁平王\">梁王（梁平王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘襄\">襄（刘襄）</span>没有好的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">师傅</span>，因而陷于不义。\"于是〖[削<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>〖$八城</span>，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任王后</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">枭首于市。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>还剩〖$十城</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘襄\">襄（刘襄）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十九年（时长）</span>去世，谥为平<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘无伤\">无伤（刘无伤）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁无伤\">梁王（梁无伤）</span>。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "济川王明",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济川</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘明\">明（刘明）</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>之子，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">桓邑侯</span>在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景（汉景帝）</span>中<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>封为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济川</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七年（时长）</span>，因<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">射</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>获罪，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>〖[请诛，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>不忍〖[诛，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘明\">明（刘明）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>。〖[迁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">房陵</span>，封地〖[收归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>为郡。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "济东王彭离",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济东</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭离\">彭离（刘彭离）</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>之子，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景（汉景帝）</span>中<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>封为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济东</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十九年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭离\">彭离（刘彭离）</span>骄横凶悍，无人君之<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>，黄昏时私下与奴仆、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亡命</span>少年<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十人</span>出行<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">抢劫<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>人，夺取财物为乐。所<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>被发现的有〖$百馀人</span>，国中都知道，无人敢夜行。被杀者的儿子〖:上书告发。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>〖[请诛，皇上不忍，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span>他为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>，〖[迁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上庸</span>，封地〖[收归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大河</span>郡。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "山阳哀王定",
      "text": "<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">山阳</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：山阳哀王\">哀王（山阳哀王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘定\">定（刘定）</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>之子，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景（汉景帝）</span>中<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>封为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山阳</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">九年（时长）</span>去世，无子，国〖[除，地〖[收归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山阳</span>郡。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "济阴哀王不识",
      "text": "<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">济阴</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：济阴哀王\">哀王（济阴哀王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘不识\">不识（刘不识）</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>之子，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景（汉景帝）</span>中<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>封为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济阴</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>去世，无子，国〖[除，地〖[收归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济阴</span>郡。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>虽然因受亲爱之故，封王在膏腴之地，但恰逢<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉家</span>国力昌盛，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>殷富，故能积累财货，广建<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宫室</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车服</span>比拟<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。但这也僭越了。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "褚先生引窦婴直谏",
      "text": "褚先生说：臣做郎官时，听宫殿中喜好事的老郎吏讲到此事。我私下认为使得<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁孝王</span>怨望、想做不善之事的，事情是从宫中生出来的。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span>是女主，因爱小儿子的缘故，想让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>不及时正言指出其不可的情状，迎合意旨草草应付，私下以获赏赐为乐，这不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">忠臣</span>。整齐如<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">魏其侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦婴</span>那样直言进谏，怎么会有后来的祸事？<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>与王<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宴见</span>，侍<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span><span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">饮</span>酒，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>说：\"千秋万岁之后把皇位传给王。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span>高兴。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦婴</span>在前，跪地说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>度，传子、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">嫡孙</span>，如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">帝（汉景帝）</span>怎能传给弟弟，擅〖[乱<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">高帝（汉高祖）</span>之约呢！\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>默然不语。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span>心中不快。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "成王戏封桐叶",
      "text": "故事说，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周成王\">成王（周成王）</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弱小弟弟</span>站在树下，取一<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">桐叶</span>给弟弟，说：\"我用这封你为侯。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>听说后，进见说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">天王</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>弟弟，很好。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周成王\">成王（周成王）</span>说：\"我不过是跟他开玩笑罢了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人主</span>没有过失之举，不应有戏言，说了就必须执行。\"于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>小弟于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">应县</span>。此后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周成王\">成王（周成王）</span>终身不敢再开玩笑，言必行。<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">孝经</span>说：\"非<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>不言，非道不行。\"这是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">圣人</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>言。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">主上</span>不宜对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>说好话。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>上有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>的倚重，骄横日久，屡次听<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>说好话，称千秋万世之后传位于王，却不真正执行。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "朝见之礼",
      "text": "又<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯王</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">朝见</span>天子，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>共应<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四次</span>相见：刚到，入小见；到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">正月朔旦</span>，献<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">皮</span>荐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">璧玉</span>贺<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">正月</span>，是法见；<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三日</span>之后，为王<span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">置酒</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赐</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金钱</span>财物；再过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二日</span>，再入小见，然后告辞。共留<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>不超过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十日</span>。小见，是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">燕见</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">禁门</span>内，在省中饮酒，不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士人</span>可以进入的。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>西<span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">来朝，因而留下，将近<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">半年</span>。入宫与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人主</span>同<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">辇</span>，出行同<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>。用大话示之以宠而实不兑现，让他说出怨言，谋<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">叛逆，然后又跟着忧虑，不是舍近求远吗！不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大贤之人</span>，不知退让。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">仪法</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">朝见</span>贺<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">正月</span>者，常是〖$一王</span>与〖$四侯</span>一同<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">朝见</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀岁</span>才一次。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>连年入<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">朝见</span>，久留。俗语说\"骄子不孝\"，不是恶言。所以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯王</span>应为他们设置良<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">师傅</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">能直言的忠臣</span>，如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汲黯</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩长孺</span>等敢直言极谏的人，怎会有祸患！"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "殷周之争",
      "text": "听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>西入<span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">朝，〖:谒<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宴见</span>中，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>一同侍坐在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>面前，私下交谈。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">帝（汉景帝）</span>说：\"我听说<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">殷道</span>亲亲，〖_周道</span>尊尊，其义一样。<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">安车</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">大驾</span>，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁孝王</span>托付给他。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span><span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">跪席起身说：\"好。\"酒宴罢后出来，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">帝（汉景帝）</span>召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>等通晓<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">经术</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>说这样的话，是什么意思？\"都答：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>意欲<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">帝（汉景帝）</span>的太子。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">帝（汉景帝）</span>问其情状，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>等说：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">殷道</span>亲亲的，立弟弟。〖_周道</span>尊尊的，立儿子。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">殷道</span>崇尚质朴，质朴者法天，亲近其亲，故立弟。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">周道</span>崇尚文饰，文者法地，尊者敬也，敬其本始，故立长子。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">周道</span>太子死，立<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">嫡孙</span>。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">殷道</span>太子死，立其弟。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">帝（汉景帝）</span>问：\"你们以为怎样？\"都答：\"如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉家</span>效法<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">周道</span>不得立弟，应当立子。所以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋宣公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋宣公</span>死，不立子而传弟。弟得国而死，又还给兄之子。弟的儿子争位，认为自己应代父，就<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>兄之子。因此国家<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">乱，祸不绝。所以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>说'<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君子</span>崇尚居正，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>之祸是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：宋宣公\">宣公（宋宣公）</span>造成的'。臣请见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>说明此事。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>等入见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>，说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>说想<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>一旦去世，要立谁？\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>说：\"我再<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">帝（汉景帝）</span>的儿子。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>等就以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋宣公</span>不立正嗣酿祸，祸〖[乱五世不绝，小不忍则害大义的事说给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>听。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>才释然，就让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>归国。但<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>听说这番话出自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>等<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>，怨恨，派人来<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>回头看他说：\"我就是所谓<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：袁盎\">袁将军（袁盎）</span>，公不会认错人吧？\"刺客说：\"正是！\"就<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span>杀了他，把<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>扔下，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>还插在身上。看那<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>，是新磨的。查问<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>中的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">磨剑工匠</span>，工匠说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">梁郎</span>某子来磨过此<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>。\"由此觉察此事，派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">使者</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追捕</span>。单是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>想◉杀</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀人</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">文吏</span>穷究其本，谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>的苗头颇为显露。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>不吃饭，日夜哭泣不止。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>非常忧虑，问<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>认为派通晓<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">经术</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吏</span>去处理，才可化解。于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕季主</span>前去办理。这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>都通<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">经术</span>，知<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">大礼</span>。回来时，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸昌厩</span>，取<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">火</span>把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>的<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>辞都〖[烧了，空手回来见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>问：\"怎样？\"答：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>不知情。造此事者，只是他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">幸臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羊胜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙诡</span>等人而已。都已〖[伏诛处死，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>无事。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>大喜，说：\"快去〖:拜谒<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>听说后，立刻起身吃饭，气色恢复。所以说，不通<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">经术</span>不懂古今<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">大礼</span>，是不能做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">三公</span>和左右<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">近臣</span>的。见识浅薄的人，就如从竹管里看天一样。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>少子，迁<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>锺爱，广建<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">睢阳</span>。 <span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旌旂</span><span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">警跸</span>，势比<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">天王</span>。 功〖[扞<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，计由孙羊。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦婴</span>正议，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>遭<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">劫</span>〖[伤。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝〖[穷查<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>狱，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">冠盖</span>相望。 祸由骄子，遂致猖狂。 虽分<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">五国</span>，最终不昌。"
    }
  }
}